oracle.pg.common

Interface OracleCSVDatatypeConstants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    OraclePropertyGraphConstants
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseCommon, OraclePropertyGraph, OraclePropertyGraphBase

    public interface OracleCSVDatatypeConstants
    This interface defines the data type constants used for CSV to PG conversion
